overview.en: ETW token is a multi chain digital wallet with global decentralized application. Relying on the credit privacy system of blockchain decentralization, ETW token provides safe and fast digital asset management services and financial privacy services for global users, and creates the world's largest digital traffic wallet.
overview.zh: ETW TOKEN是一款全球去中心化应用的多链数字化钱包，是依托区块链去中心化的信用隐私体系，为全球用户提供安全快捷的数字资产管理服务和金融隐私服务，打造全球最大的数字流量钱包。
